main event: Two UFO sightings were reported by a Colombian Navy vessel near Cartagena, Colombia on October 19, 1959.
interesting points: The first sighting was at 19/1158Z with an azimuth of 270 degrees,The objects appeared slightly darker and larger than stars,The objects were described as similar to an artificial satellite,One of the sightings involved an orange luminous body with a circular form,No additional data was available for further evaluation.
sighted object: two unidentified flying objects described as orange luminous bodies
